---
title: Easy Creamy Tomato, Mushroom & Chorizo Penne with Rocket & Parmesan Salad
description: Golden pipes of penne combine with rich tomato paste, cream and smokey chorizo to create an elegant meal fit for only the best. Add
sharp Parmesan and a rocket salad for crunch and dinner is complete.
